    <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">Most gastric sleeve patients return to light activities in 1-2 weeks, full activities in 6-8 weeks. Complete healing takes 6 weeks, though you'll feel significantly better by Week 4. Timeline varies by individual, job type, and adherence to post-op guidelines.</p>
